reviews: Works well for my surveillance camera. No hiccups.

Amazing camera for the price. I was skeptical, did few weeks research. No monthly payments, app is easy to use, good features, always updating. I have camera 40ft away from Wi-fi router/outside. Camera picks up signal fine even with a few solid walls inbetween it and router. Bought outdoor housing/micro sd separate, everything’s running slick. So far I would recommend. Will update if any troubles.
Arrived today, had camera mounted within 20 minutes. Came with all hardware, no issues with sound or picture. Would recommend.
Shipped/Delivered as expected. I got a big head so took some time to stretch the walls out. Worth every dollhair.

Great quality battery. Some have complained about charger. For me it’s not an issue, seems to be built well and charges batteries over night. These batteries would get 5 stars if they could hold a higher charge for longer on high draining devices like headlamps or controllers being constantly used. I will be buying a few more sets of the AA+AAA on the near future.

Cheers Panasonic
Can’t get a better light bar for the price. Been threw snow/mud/rain. Down to -40c no problems. Cooling fans are adequate enough to do their job. I’d buy another, or two.

Awesome little radio. Great features - Alarm for calling - Flashlight with strobe function - Radio. Can save many preset stations. Built very well, great quality.
I’d buy another, or two. Cheers Baofeng.
